{
  "stem": "1033.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the pleasant thing that we all wanted to believe, in spite of the horrible stories that people whispered about-- of people being shot, people being asked to dig their graves, and then they were shut into it.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was not unknown.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I certainly never believed it, not until when I saw that amazing movie.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and, and, and like, like a cold wave coming over me, it was precisely like that, when you see those people coming in with their suitcases and giving their names proudly-- Rosenberg, Wasserman-- and walking away with their paper stamped.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when you see the-- two months later-- the suitcases being empty, thrown out of the window, and these people are like nothing-- like flotsam and jetsam, like nothings.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and, and, and the world goes on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the little voice inside every one of us-- certainly inside me, and all of us-- keeps asking questions, keeps wondering why, keeps wondering how could we make it better?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How could something like this gone on and how-- excuse me-- how a thing like this must never, ever go on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Going back again, you said that you were quite sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened to you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as we got to-- I didn't know it was Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got in this place at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we heard some-- by, by then, we all knew-- like, through seven layers of fog-- we knew that the war was coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was some commotion in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I ran to the-- to the-- to the fence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by then, the fence was not electrified and put the-- I-- you know, and I grabbed the fence.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I saw soldiers coming in.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
